Album artist

for Euclid:
    artist.type: string, -z artist
    artist.default: 'artist'

=item --album [=] <album>

Album name

for Euclid:
    album.type: string, -z album
    album.default: 'album'

=item --year [=] <year>

Album release year

=for Euclid:
    year.type: /[0-9]{4}/

=item --version

=item --usage

=item --help

=item --man

Print the usual program information

=back

